scrying
Level-5th
CastingTime-10Minutes
Range/Area-Self
School-Divination
Attack/Save-WIS
OtherInfo-                You can see and hear a articular creature you choose that is on the same lane of existence as you. The target must make a Wisdom saving throw, which is modified by how well you know the target and the sort of hysical connection you have to it. If a target knows you're casting this sell, it can fail the saving throw voluntarily if it wants to be observed.
